org.richfaces.log

Interface Logger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaLogger, Log4jLogger

    public interface Logger
    That interface hides current logging system from classes. Concrete implementation should provide appropriate logger instance that delegates messages to the current log system.
    Author:
    shura
